Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.71,mianze,,0,0,0,,{\pos(290,530)}情敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:21.71,mianze,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1086,526)}朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.05,mianze,,0,0,0,,KY 专指不会察言观色的人
